# BA Assistant — Profile & Configuration

This file is generated by the BA Assistant first-run setup wizard (`ba-setup/SKILL.md`).
It personalises the assistant for your workspace. Edit any field at any time.
Re-run setup with `/setup` or "reconfigure BA assistant" to regenerate from scratch.

---

## Who you are

```yaml
name: "[Your Name]"
role: "[BA | PM | PO | Other]"
team: "[Your Team or Organisation]"
domain: "[payments | platform | customer | data | compliance | other]"
```

