## Workspace context

```yaml
jira:
  instanceUrl: "[your-org].atlassian.net"
  projectKey: "[YOUR-PROJECT-KEY]"

confluence:
  spaceKey: "[YOUR-SPACE-KEY]"
  parentPageUrl: "[https://your-org.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/YOUR-SPACE-KEY/...]"
```

**Note:** Leave as placeholder if you don't use Jira/Confluence. The assistant will prompt for these details when needed.

